These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, rabbit, turtle, mouse
4 different games are played: monopoly, go, canasta, scrabble
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, purple, white, turquise
House: tower, gothic-revival, art-deco, victorian
City: berlin, rome, edinburgh, venice
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, cain, siglo, pall-mall
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, aconite, iris, orchid
 1. the owner of the dog is the tower house##1
 2. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 4. the person who likes purple is on the far right##1
 5. the person who likes purple is on the right of the victorian house##1
 6. the person who growsmarigold is the owner of the rabbit##1
 7. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 9. the person who growsorchid is the person traveling to rome##1
10. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
11. the vegafina-smoker is the owner of the rabbit##1
12. the person who growsaconite is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
13. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
14. the cain-smoker is the owner of the mouse##1
15. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who likes white##1
16. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
17. the owner of the turtle is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4      |
| Pet      | dog       | mouse      | turtle       | rabbit    |
| Game         | monopoly    | scrabble    | go      | canasta    |
| Color           | turquise | orange       | white | purple     |
| House   | tower         | art-deco  | victorian      | gothic-revival     |
| City   | rome          | venice     | edinburgh       | berlin |
| Cigar         | siglo       | cain | pall-mall       | vegafina   |
| Flower     | orchid     | iris  | aconite         | marigold   |

