There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda, tea, hot-chocolate
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, davidoff, pall-mall, fonseca
House: colonial, farmhouse, cottage, cape-cod
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, january, february, june
4 different games are played: backgammon, canasta, monopoly, go
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, blue, red, pink
 1. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the cottage house##1
 3. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 4. the cottage house is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 5. the cape-cod house is the davidoff-smoker##1
 6. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 7. the colonial house is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
11. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
12. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
13. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
14. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
15. the person playing go is on the far left##1
16. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
17. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3      |      4      |
