The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, marigold, azalea, zinnia
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, 7up, fanta, cola
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, tram, motorbike, car
4 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg, chess, go
 1. the person playing whist is on the right of the cottage house##1
