 7. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 8. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
10. the person driving the car is the person who growsmarigold##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is the craftsman house##1
12. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person driving the car##1
13. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
14. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
15. the prince-smoker is the person drinking cola##1
16. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
17. the person playing chess is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
